These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Food: strawberry, spinach, cherry, cauliflower
Cigar: dannemann, aristoff, bongani, havana
1. Cigar:havana is on the left of Food:cherry##1
2. Food:strawberry is on the left of Cigar:aristoff##1
3. Food:cauliflower is in an odd position##4
4. Cigar:bongani is on the left or right of Cigar:havana##3
5. Food:strawberry is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Food   | strawberry | spinach | cauliflower | cherry |
| Cigar        | dannemann | aristoff   | havana | bongani    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Sport: soccer, basketball, skateboarding, golf
Birthday: september, december, august, october
1. Sport:basketball is on the left of Sport:golf##1
2. Birthday:september is on the left of Birthday:august##1
3. Birthday:august is in an odd position##4
4. Birthday:september == Sport:soccer##1
5. Birthday:december is on the right of Birthday:august##1
6. Birthday:september == Sport:soccer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Sport   | skateboarding | soccer  | basketball  | golf |
| Birthday   | october    | september | august | december    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Color: chestnut, lilac, mauve, apricot
Cigar: davidoff, old-henry, pall-mall, chaman
1. Color:apricot is on the left or right of Cigar:chaman##3
2. Color:mauve is in an even position##4
3. Cigar:chaman is on the left or right of Color:lilac##3
4. Cigar:chaman is on the right of Cigar:pall-mall##1
5. Cigar:davidoff is in an odd position##4
6. Color:lilac is on the right of Color:mauve##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Color          | apricot | mauve | lilac    | chestnut      |
| Cigar   | pall-mall        | chaman     | davidoff | old-henry |

