.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Birthday: october, june, december, july
Cigar: cain, old-henry, baccarat, ritmeester
1. Birthday:june is between Cigar:cain and Cigar:ritmeester##2
2. Birthday:july is on the left of Birthday:october##1
3. Cigar:baccarat is in an odd position##4
4. Cigar:old-henry is on the left of Cigar:ritmeester##1
5. Cigar:old-henry is on the right of Birthday:october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Birthday         | july | october | june | december |
| Cigar   | baccarat       | cain   | old-henry    | ritmeester  |

