.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Beverage: fanta, sprite, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
Color: amber, grey, coral, ivory
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the right of Color:ivory##1
2. Color:grey == Beverage:almond-milk##1
3. Color:coral is on the right of Beverage:fanta##1
4. Beverage:sprite is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:hot-chocolate is in an odd position##4
6. Color:amber is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | sprite  | fanta    | hot-chocolate   | almond-milk       |
| Color   | amber | ivory | coral | grey |

