.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
City: edinburgh, london, liverpool, boston
Transport: quad-bike, helicopter, motorbike, bus
1. Transport:bus is on the left or right of City:london##3
2. City:boston is in an odd position##4
3. Transport:bus is on the left or right of City:boston##3
4. City:boston is on the right of Transport:bus##1
5. City:edinburgh is between City:boston and City:london##2
6. Transport:helicopter is in an odd position##4
7. Transport:helicopter is between City:edinburgh and Transport:motorbike##2
8. City:edinburgh is on the left or right of City:london##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| City   | london | edinburgh      | boston | liverpool |
| Transport   | quad-bike  | bus | helicopter    | motorbike            |

