.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
Beverage: 7up, lemonade, hot-chocolate, tea
Music-Genre: trance, d&b, metal, salsa
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Beverage:7up##3
2. Beverage:7up is on the right of Beverage:lemonade##1
3. Music-Genre:trance is between Music-Genre:d&b and Beverage:hot-chocolate##2
4. Music-Genre:trance is in an odd position##4
5. Beverage:hot-chocolate == Music-Genre:metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | tea | lemonade   | 7up | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre    | salsa     | d&b | trance     | metal  |

