Transport: quad-bike, helicopter, airplane, motorbike
1. Color:purple == Transport:motorbike##1
2. Transport:quad-bike is on the right of Color:purple##1
3. Transport:motorbike is between Transport:quad-bike and Color:brown##2
4. Color:purple is in an odd position##4
5. Transport:motorbike is on the left or right of Transport:quad-bike##3
6. Color:pink is on the left or right of Transport:helicopter##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Color      | pink       | brown   | purple | amber |
| Transport   | airplane | helicopter | motorbike        | quad-bike    |

