.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
Transport: ship, subway, bike, train
Music-Genre: gospel, folk, house, hip-hop
1. Music-Genre:folk is on the far left##1
2. Transport:bike is on the left or right of Transport:ship##3
3. Transport:train is on the far left or far right##3
4. Music-Genre:house is on the left of Music-Genre:hip-hop##1
5. Music-Genre:hip-hop is on the right of Transport:ship##1
6. Music-Genre:house is in an even position##4
7. Music-Genre:gospel == Transport:subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Transport   | train | ship    | bike       | subway |
| Music-Genre       | folk  | house | hip-hop | gospel  |

